Abstract.Para: The T233 package for GAP provides tools for the classification of tensors in the vector space V = ℱ_q^2 ⊗ ℱ_q^3 ⊗ ℱ_q^3 over finite fields. This package allows users to compute the rank and orbit of tensors within this space, aiding in research in combinatorics, Galois geometry and algebraic structures.
